{"tid":877880,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"考得唔好入唔到U有咩問題啫?","createTime":"2018-10-26T16:36:24.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-26T17:30:06.000Z","uid":54270,"like":7,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"546bef59d5bdf62cae78c887a310d6758ba4637b","tid":877880,"uid":54270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T16:36:24.000Z","msg":"條條大路通羅馬啊 <br />\nFor example<br />\n<br />\n[能仁推出學費全免/半免學費獎學金計劃]<br />\n<br />\n為鼓勵同學完成本地學士學位課程，能仁推出學費全免/半免學費獎學金計劃。如有DSE 33222 成績報讀本校2018-19年度任何學士學位課程，除獲得政府三萬零八百元資助，其餘學費可獲本校豁免，直至畢業為止，為期四年。<br />\n<br />\n如非DSE 33222 成績入讀，則可獲半免學費的獎學金至畢業為止，為期四年。<br />\n<br />\n此外學院還有其他助學金協助同學，可以減輕學費負擔，專心完成學士學位課程。<br />\n想了解更多，請即致電3996 1000 / 3996 1001 或上網報名 <a href=\"http://ny.edu.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fny.edu.hk&d=GcW%2FYzJcQwdv7NKnLRP%2BTNtKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=db0edfc1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">ny.edu.hk</a>。<br />\n<br />\n主要學科包括中文，會計，英文，商科，社工。<br />\n<br />\n社工加開傍晚周末班，方便在職人仕。"},{"pid":"5052a61094227005c10310fbcb62a43959f17e54","tid":877880,"uid":211528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T16:38:55.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"72e95646146a6f3e7a45337782e5423638fb167c","tid":877880,"uid":198998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5052a61094227005c10310fbcb62a43959f17e54","tid":877880,"uid":211528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T16:38:55.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T16:40:22.000Z","msg":"巴打轉戰校園台?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c8e12d5f7094df15bb1077d4eef710999bca05e","tid":877880,"uid":54270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5052a61094227005c10310fbcb62a43959f17e54","tid":877880,"uid":211528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T16:38:55.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T16:40:41.000Z","msg":"同學咩系 GE同一組吖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\"